The epsilon Pareto thresholds are:
SAT: 1%

Given the variance in evaluations, even though gpt-oss-20b has average accuracies of 98.5% (SAT), 94% (ABD), and 71% (DED), individual evaluations can fluctuate—e.g., reaching 99.1% (SAT), 95.5% (ABD), and 73.6% (DED) currently.

ABD > 93.75%
